data.eml:eml: Discovery of two new species of Alucitidae (Lepidoptera) from Vietnam

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Byun, Bong-Kyu, Park, Kyu-Tek (2007): Discovery of two new species of Alucitidae (Lepidoptera) from Vietnam. Zootaxa 1390: 51-57, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175221
